Streamline Integration Callouts with Integration Orchestration

Use Integration Orchestration to dynamically create integration callout plans, and enable users to review the status of integrations with different external endpoints. Users can easily track the progress of all integration callouts, resulting in better process visibility and efficiency.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.
title: Streamline Integration Callouts with Salesforce Orchestration
